        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nhi Sylvain Desbureaux, this component is contributed by vendor, \nthere's a tomcat server AND a mysql server on the same container? Yes\nonap user shouldn't have passwordless sudo capabilities - we add sudo capabilties to ensure have start mysql permission.",
